To make dressing: In a blender or a food processor with a metal blade, puree 8 orange slices (reserve the remainder for the salad). Add olive oil, sugar, salt, vinegar, and hot pepper sauce. Process until pureed. Makes 1/2 cup. To make salad: In a medium-size bowl, toss spinach, almonds, remaining oranges, and onion slices with dressing. Serve immediately.